# 3. Component Design Rules

When implementing UI:

### Prefer reusable components

Instead of:
Hardcoded UI inside page

Use:

Reusable component

Example:

Bad:

UserPage.vue
inline avatar + name layout

Good:

components/UserAvatar.vue
components/UserCard.vue

---

### Naming conventions

Component names must be:

PascalCase

Example:

UserCard.vue
DashboardWidget.vue
NotificationPanel.vue

